 'aging.' But if you grind down your teeth faster, you 'age' faster. The good part is you can reverse the process by using the same physics in reverse, i.e., you 'add' height back to the teeth.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglvzdsR308_text","label":"gglvzdsR308_text","default":"<p>Over 20,000 people have started using the appliance and this method since late 2024.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwrz9alfgC_text","label":"ggwrz9alfgC_text","default":"<p>Note that there is a 'Size chart' above that you should refer to for measurements of our appliances.</p><p>We recommend choosing size based on the instructions in this video (<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?si=YPejTMYZqcjja8qg&amp;v=9gVyEOWx-AE&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\"><u>link</u></a>)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4xGGySst3_text","label":"gg4xGGySst3_text","default":"<p>Please refer the image above where we compare R3 to R1 and R2.</p><p>Note that you can start with R3 and our appliances do not go in any particular order.</p><p><strong>Guarantee</strong>: R1 has no guarantee.&nbsp; Both R2 &amp; R3 are guaranteed for one year with one free replacement. This replacement warranty is limited to one user per customer and doesn't cover repeat purchases of the same appliance.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0_CgBP22v_text","label":"gg0_CgBP22v_text","default":"<p>It is made out of 100% food grade silicone.</p>"}],
